L/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong>HTML <code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code> 요소</strong>는 안쪽의 텍스트가 긴 인용문임을 나타냅니다. 주로 들여쓰기를 한 것으로 그려집니다. (외형을 바꾸는 법은 <a href=\"#사용_일람\">사용 일람</a>을 참고하세요) 인용문의 출처 URL은 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/blockquote#attr-cite\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>cite</code></a> 특성으로, 출처 텍스트는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/cite\"><code>&lt;cite&gt;</code></a> 요소로 제공할 수 있습니다.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"445\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/tabbed/blockquote.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>\n\n<p class=\"hidden\">The source for this interactive example is stored in a GitHub repository. If you'd like to contribute to the interactive examples project, please clone <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/interactive-examples\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">https://github.com/mdn/interactive-examples </a> and send us a pull request.</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\">콘텐츠 카테고리</a></th>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#%ed%94%8c%eb%a1%9c%ec%9a%b0_%ec%bd%98%ed%85%90%ec%b8%a0\">플로우 콘텐츠</a>, 구획 루트, 뚜렷한 콘텐츠.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">가능한 콘텐츠</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#%ed%94%8c%eb%a1%9c%ec%9a%b0_%ec%bd%98%ed%85%90%ec%b8%a0\">플로우 콘텐츠</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">태그 생략</th>\n   <td>None, both the starting and ending tag are mandatory.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">가능한 부모 요소</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#%ed%94%8c%eb%a1%9c%ec%9a%b0_%ec%bd%98%ed%85%90%ec%b8%a0\">플로우 콘텐츠</a>를 허용하는 모든 요소</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">암시적 ARIA 역할</th>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html-aria/#dfn-no-corresponding-role\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">대응하는 역할 없음</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">가능한 ARIA 역할</th>\n   <td>모두</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">DOM 인터페이스</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLQuoteElement\"><code>HTMLQuoteElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"특성","title":"특성","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">이 요소는 </span><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">전역 특성</a>을 포함합니다.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"cite\"><a id=\"attr-cite\" href=\"#attr-cite\"><b><code>cite</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>인용문의 출처 문서나 메시지를 가리키는 URL. 인용문의 맥락 혹은 출처 정보를 가리킬 용도입니다.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"사용_일람","title":"사용 일람","isH3":false,"content":"<p>인용문의 들여쓰기를 바꾸려면 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/CSS\">CSS</a> <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/margin-left\"><code>margin-left</code></a>와 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/margin-right\"><code>margin-right</code></a>, 혹은 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/margin\"><code>margin</code></a> 단축 속성을 사용하세요.</p>\n\n<p>별도의 블록을 쓰지 않아도 될 짧은 인용문은 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/q\"><code>&lt;q&gt;</code></a> 요소를 사용하세요.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"예제","title":"예제","isH3":false,"content":"<p>다음 예제는 <code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code> 요소를 사용해 <a href=\"https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc1149\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 1149</a> <cite>A Standard for the Transmission of IP Datagrams on Avian Carriers의 문단을 인용합니다.</cite></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>blockquote</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">cite</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1149<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Avian carriers can provide high delay, low\n  throughput, and low altitude service.  The\n  connection topology is limited to a single\n  point-to-point path for each carrier, used with\n  standard carriers, but many carriers can be used\n  without significant interference with each other,\n  outside of early spring.  This is because of the 3D\n  ether space available to the carriers, in contrast\n  to the 1D ether used by IEEE802.3.  The carriers\n  have an intrinsic collision avoidance system, which\n  increases availability.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>blockquote</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"예제 sample\" id=\"frame_예제\" width=\"640\" height=\"180\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/blockquote/_sample_.%EC%98%88%EC%A0%9C.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"명세","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/grouping-content.html#the-blockquote-element","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"html.elements.blockquote"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.blockquote","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/blockquote/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"같이_보기","title":"같이 보기","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>인라인 인용문을 위한 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/q\"><code>&lt;q&gt;</code></a> 요소.</li>\n <li>인용문 출처 표기를 위한 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/cite\"><code>&lt;cite&gt;</code></a> 요소.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"특성","id":"특성"},{"text":"사용 일람","id":"사용_일람"},{"text":"예제","id":"예제"},{"text":"명세","id":"specifications"},{"text":"브라우저 호환성","id":"브라우저_호환성"},{"text":"같이 보기","id":"같이_보기"}],"summary":"HTML <blockquote> 요소는 안쪽의 텍스트가 긴 인용문임을 나타냅니다. 주로 들여쓰기를 한 것으로 그려집니다. (외형을 바꾸는 법은 사용 일람을 참고하세요) 인용문의 출처 URL은 cite 특성으로, 출처 텍스트는 <cite> 요소로 제공할 수 있습니다.","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<blockquote>: The Block Quotation element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"blockquote","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<blockquote> : l'élément de bloc de citation","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<blockquote>: ブロック引用要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<blockquote>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<blockquote>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<blockquote>：块级引用元素","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"<blockquote>","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/html/element/blockquote","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/html/element/blockquote/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Hypertext Markup Language"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"HTML 요소 참고서"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/blockquote","title":"<blockquote>: 인용 블록 요소"}],"pageTitle":"<blockquote>: 인용 블록 요소 - HTML: Hypertext Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}